# Step 7: Deployment Detail & Build Logs Page UI

**Phase:** 6, Step 7
**Status:** Not Started
**Depends on:** Step 2 (deployments API), Step 5 (StatusBadge component), Step 6 (deployment-row component, layout with tabs)
**Blocks:** None directly (Phase 7 will add preview deployment UI using these components)

---

## Goal

Build the deployment history page showing all deployments with filtering and pagination, and the individual deployment detail page with build log rendering, ANSI color support, deployment metadata, and a status timeline. After this step, users can browse deployment history and inspect build logs for any deployment.

